moa.options

Class WEKAClassOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • moa.AbstractMOAObject
      • moa.options.AbstractOption
        • moa.options.AbstractClassOption
          • moa.options.WEKAClassOption
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, MOAObject, Option

    public class WEKAClassOption
extends AbstractClassOption
    WEKA class option. This option is used to access options in WEKA. For example, WEKAClassifier uses it to set the base learner.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
